c63488a5-cee0-4ac0-8f3f-d0bdd54aa23b.text: the first is the logic of one of the most interesting tools of the past decade. "Word2Vec"Word2vec is more of a concept- using a group of related models that are used to produce word embeddings in some latent space. These models are shallow, often only two-layer-deep neural networks that are trained to reconstruct linguistic contexts of words and represent those contexts as vectors in the latent space. Word2vec models generally take in a large corpus of text and produces this vector space, typically of several hundred dimensions, with each unique word in the corpus being assigned a corresponding vector in the space. Word vectors are positioned in the vector space such that words that share common contexts in the corpus are located in close proximity to one another in the space. This has the shocking effect of producing meaning in the space. Famously, the vector for the word "man" plus the word "royal" gets you (near) the vector for the word "king": a "royal" "man". Word2vec was created by researchers at Google and introduced in a 2013 paper titled "Efficient Estimation of Word Representations in Vector Space". The model has since been improved and extended upon, with the most notable extension being the development of the "Global Vectors for Word Representation" (GloVe) model by researchers at Stanford University. The technology is totally open source, and can be used with the python package "Gensim". Go on, try it out yourself.This technology  been widely used for a variety of natural language processing tasks and has been shown to produce state-of-the-art performance on tasks such as language modeling and syntactic parsing, even nearly a decade after the technique was first implemented. What is so fascinating about the w2v embedding space is the implication of mathematical relationships between not just words, but between _concepts_. #Dive into the psychological implications

b3ac6223-dd0e-4f09-82b3-714d742a5ab2.text: Forewarning of disruptive events is of paramount importance to logistics management and supply-chain protection. In recent years we have seen the fragility of our global supply chain networks and the pitfalls of just-in-time manufacturing practices. These vulnerabilities underscore the importance of pro-active protection of supply chains. Stave's predictions provide quantitative risk assessment metrics in cities around the world, which can facilitate management processes to identify potential vulnerabilities and prioritize protective measures. Typically this involves analysis of key locations, modes of transportation, and other factors that make up a supply chain, as well as the likelihood and potential impact of various threats.Another important measure is to implement measures to reduce the risk of damage or disruption to key infrastructure, such as transportation networks, warehouses, and other facilities. Given forewarning of events appropriate insurance coverage may be established, and appropriate protective measures may be taken. This could involve implementing security measures, such as perimeter fencing in the case of riots, or access controls and surveillance systems in the case of bombings, or even rerouting of supplies to avoid a region moving down the path of instability and upheaval.It is also important to have contingency plans in place to allow for the continuation of operations in the event of a disruption. This might involve identifying alternative sources of supplies or transportation routes, or implementing processes to quickly recover from a disruption.Finally, it is important to be aware of the potential for terrorism and other threats, and to remain vigilant and prepared to respond to any potential incidents. This might involve working with local authorities and other stakeholders to develop response plans and procedures, and training staff on how to recognize and report potential threats.

a68b2e83-31b7-4a68-8087-d34db19c5408.text: When all the building blocks are in play, near each other, it takes near no effort to start the inevitable. Pushing a boulder down the other side of a hill that took generations to push up one side. This is where we currently stand- or stood before. We have already made first contact. The well-known Fermi Paradox is a list of assertions that are winking and nodding us toward the overwhelming likelihood of alien life. There exist billions of stars within the Milky Way, planets in habitable zones around those stars are actually extremely common, most of which are much older than the Earth & Sol. There is likely nothing inherently special about us to have developed intelligent life. Despite vast distances, radio waves could be sent out and provide notice of life. Probes sent out by civilizations millions of years older than ours should litter the galaxy. 						 But there is, to date, no compelling evidence of alien life. Every method that we have used in this search has been either optical telescope based, or radio wave based. These are reasonable starting points, as we ourselves shine in RF space, and we assume any intelligent life must also have figured out RF communication. We’re looking for us. One potential answer is that we aren’t looking in the right spaces, or rather, that our concept of “alien” isn’t alien enough. I don’t mean “the right part of space”, I mean the “right space” in the physicist’s sense: 3-space, 4-space, Minkowski-space[^1]. We are simply looking for a mode of existence which is outmoded. 4665914d-667f-43e8-bbfb-13e213b3864e.text: The typical American understanding of the [[Dharma]] and [[Karma]] from Vedic traditions is incorrect. Karma is not a witch's "law of thirds" where every misdeed is repaid three times over to the actor. Nothing so paltry. The common vedic understanding is also incorrect, but it is closer. When we come into this life, we come in with a *vector*. This vector is the dharma, and has direction and magnitude, being a vector after all. The direction is the optimal path one can traverse in this life. You can do no better than your dharma. Karma then is the displacement force your actions have on your future possible dharma. At each point in time, your dharma changes according to your actions. so called "good karma" brings your closer into alignment with your dharma, and "bad karma" brings you our of alignment. Baked into the concept of the dharma is this idea of optimality- that there is a defined purpose and evaluated optimum "trajectory" of your life. This is the dharmoid path. All statements of good or bad behavior, karma,  action, are in reference to the optimum. And how do we define the optimum? There then must be introduced [[Samsara]]. The cycle of reincarnation. The soul follows a specific path around the skin, which is to say the surface, but sometimes a little deeper, of the dharmoid. Here, the dharmoid is displayed as a torus, but in all likelyhood the path is more akin to a hyperdimensional toroid. The path in gold is the path of an individual soul- a closed path is an unthinking actor- because a closed path is a loop. Unchanging. The phenomena of our reality is an effect of the convergence of souls on the dharmoid path. The diagram as displayed shows a single, solitary person. In reality, the interrior of the shape is a cacophany of different paths, of different souls converging. 585c7e07-9574-4752-8485-2f5763a1cf71.text: Divination does not occur when the rune is cast, when the intestines are spilled, or when the tea-leaves settle. It happens when the diviner gazes upon the field and relearns how to read. It happens in the mind of the diviner. You could just as easily prophecize with the static from an old TV as you could with guts of god-fowl. It is the discovery of reading that is the magic, it is the transition from the mundane through the noetic space to glimpse the underlying structure before re-applying it to message that contains the "magic". The diviner casts the runes, watches them fall, remembers the connections, edges, wires, chords, sympathetic vibrations, what is is like to hurtle throught he abyss of uncertainty, eyes wide and virgin again to the hands of gods. He is thus made exposed and open, and vulnerable to influence. Divination is feminine. The diviner does now apply order to the stage, the stage is a play for the onlooker- be that onlooker the diviner himself or otherwise- to ascribe some mechanism to the phenomena. "It worked because I did this".It worked because it was looking at you and you lay prostrate.

cb5bb976-93e1-45c0-b811-a3a72b48d80c.text: It is worth remembering that “Magic” has its etymological roots in “ability”, in the sense that “a magic is a thing that is able, functions”.Of the knowable magics, there are 4 that stand apart from the others. They are [[Sacrifice]], [[Agreement]], [[Volition]], and the [[Word]]

fbe9c0e2-c304-4bbb-a906-370b988a8437.text: Sacrifice is the [[Magic]] of displacement. It is the displacement forward in time of anything potential in order to increase it. Potentially increase it, that is. Sometimes trivially understood as "delayed gratification", Sacrifice is a fundamental interaction mechanism with reality. When first discovered, it is believed that the first [[Magic|magicians]] of Sacrifice believed their offerings to the future to be fulfilled in some sense- a transaction that implies another end of the deal, an entity which, because it seemingly could influence all things, must be all powerful, and because it worked through unknowable means, must know all, and so they believed this functionary to be their [[Idol|God]]. In the modern era, instead of attributing this function to the divine, we attribute it to math and expected values and probability fields. This in no way decreases its divinity. Today, most comonly, the function of sacrifice is tied directly into the fabric of society. We use it when we go to work and expect a paycheque. In some sense it is even Sacrifice that allows for more complex social relationships. Most lucratively, Sacrifice may be quantized in the form of interest yeilding assets, and these are controlled by the "Wizards of Lucre", the "Magicians of Sacrifice", and "Investment Bankers".

47c2b548-ec57-4713-9e42-1bde4b8c0d66.text: The mechanism of magic is indelibly tied to volition. The sacrifice must be made willingly, the agreement must not be coerced. It is that the very Land itself holds power. Aeon and age ago, the Land, that is to say, all the things that we know to be things, were made by God. They are in many ways, the body of God. And bestowed to us. Man is given dominion over the land, over the Body of God. To make a sacrifice, to something perhaps not of God, then requires volition. Volition is the mechanism by which we interact with not just God, but with all entities, [[Idol]]s included. Volition is the Starry Lock Qutub. It is the point of transformation, and sacrifice is the Agreement to co-orient powers. Volition is the mechanism of transformation. Engagement in transformation with an [[Idol]], Egregore, or God, orients the "blast cone" of your Qutub to the entity's input, and, according to the Agreement, theirs to yours. Sacrifice requires Volition, Communication, and Agreement. The [[Agreement]] is the mutual engagement of volition. Volition eschews karma. Not God nor any of God's creations or ilk are immune to karma, but may not generate their own. this is the special prowess of man. Volition is not a pull, volition is not a push, volition is the internal acceleration that is entirely intrinsic.

Flying through the rift hand in hand, surfing on the perfect wave next to her. His face flushed and he pushed his tongue against the roof of his mouth, pushing down the emotion. Now was time for work. Leon peeled the new propeller from the 3D printer bed. Interlocking smooth curves, a maille of torus blades designed to withstand the force his Hawk needed to operate. He slowly fitted the propeller into the central cavity of his drone. The Hawk wasn't so much a model of drone as a concept. In the aftermath of the Russo-German Police Altercation (war), the black market was flooded with one of the most effective tools levied in the conflict. Night Hawk Drone Platforms, or simply Hawks, were initially utilized as reconnaissance units. Loaded down with camera equipment you could see anything, some modules added point-field lidar and streamed up to the second spatial information to an intelligence officer. Leon's carried a gun. The new rotor was quieter, offered more thrust. Win win, becuase that is what he needed. And that is what tonight needed. His coworkers told him once to not learn about his targets lives. That coworker was now spending a life sentence in federal prison. Leon got involved, he studied his targets for days, or months if the contract allowed for it. On the edge of the forest, where they can still make it home. The zone of proximal development is where the heart lies just outside the body. External locus of control. Every fiber yearns to hold her back in, safe, close to- well- itself. The heart ripped outside of itself  casting a prismatic rainbow of sanguine self.Ape of time. I thought it would help. I, like her, knew from the start. I was weak, and now, as I sip in the dark, have only myself to know and to see. The claws remain. It sits on my mantle. cbbe569f-844c-4236-8987-7c701bae66d0.text: I didn't reject Christ, nothing so crass. In fact, I invoked his name only a few days ago. Weeks. Sleeping, restless. A spiral of thoughts turns into voices. Two, talking to each other. I can't tell about what, but I believe they are talking about me. Not audible, but almost. In a liminal space of auditory effect. I don't have time for schizophrenia. A cross, in my nightstand, in my hand, against my brow "By the power of Christ, I banish you". Demons aeresolized. Voices calmed. So you see, it isn't like I don't like Jesus. But I can't. Can't what? Do I fear the placidity of peace I expect it to bring? That I'll be one-note? Absolved and absorbed? Loss of self. Nothing so crass. I knew a man, we'll call him James, with for all intents and purposes a perfect life. A beautiful loving wife, 3 kids, and a house on a hill in the country. Lovely man. Absolutely possessed. 70-80% of the man is his adoration. Its inhuman to me. So what, I want to retain individuality? Its a good reason to not do heroin too, you know. The kingdom of heaven in a powder. I don't touch the stuff.

Description is Death. Safety is Surrender.

I don’t want safety; I want truth. I don’t want truth; I want genuine, all consuming, anything.

The truth is that I am a god. 

You can’t feel psychic pressure but you can feel it streaming out from my eyes into the fire. Into yours. I am a god in the way that you must be. “I am a mammal” in a spiritual sense. Animal is to man as man is to god, but evolution is real.  It is all one trajectory.
